                                <h2>Welcome to Buffalo's Mechanical, Inc. Meet our team!</h2>
                                <p>
                                    Buffalo's Mechanical, Inc. is a commercial/industrial Mechanical Contractor serving Northern/Central California by      
                                    providing quality HVAC construction and service since 1995. Our company philosophy is simple... provide quality                                            work, on time, at a competitive price.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    We specialize in fast track projects and high end retail. We understand the tough demands of today's construction                                           projects inclduing fiscal and scheduling demands. We are here to help you to meet those goals.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Buffalo’s is located in Northern California with offices in the Central Valley (Ripon) and the San Francisco Bay Area                                         (Sunnyvale). Our territory is from Bakersfield through Northern California, which includes The Bay Area, Central                                                California, and Sacramento.
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                  Our offices, trucks and team are equipped with the latest technology. We have the latest PC's and Apple Desktops, mobile devices, cable internet, and full color plotters for printing at our facilities. We utilize the latest software and technology handling all facets of our business and have the capability of reading and printing any digital format files. 
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    Our Field Superintendents and foreman also have the latest communication devices (Iphones/Ipads/Droids) to insure that they are able to communicate quickly from anywhere in the state. They utilize tablets to always have the latest set of plans and the ability to create field reports and take photos/videos instantly. We also have GPS trackers on all company vehcichles which are monitored 24 hours a day. They are watched daily by the managers in our offices. Our ultimate goal has always been  to be a state of the art company and build long-term partnerships with our clients, vendors and employees.                                 
                                </p>
